Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜想逃離亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.87,0:01:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓走洗達當人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.83,0:01:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加上敵人的集體攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.78,0:01:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.71,0:01:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還多了米查那個古怪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.15,0:01:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使ZZ高達的合體一波三折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.10,0:01:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,遇到的障礙愈多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.52,0:01:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我越是有所成長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.38,0:01:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可算是神給我的考驗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.05,0:01:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十八話 哈曼的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.38,0:02:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人似乎很喜歡夏日\n以前就這樣吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的,最近一直...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.62,0:02:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時冬天的寒冷也不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.99,0:02:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明大人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.31,0:03:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?叫他進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.34,0:03:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了,古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的活躍表現我聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,我把安多拉弄沉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.97,0:03:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來真是慚愧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.55,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在意\n當成負高額保險費就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.28,0:03:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,港口那邊似乎很熱鬧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.74,0:03:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主力部隊在做降落地球的準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.35,0:03:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人要親臨地球?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.55,0:03:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去,會提高士氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泰坦斯已經滅亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.46,0:03:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧干的組織也疲弱不堪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.78,0:03:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再敵對勢力都再減弱的現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是打敗地球聯邦政府的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.87,0:03:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此,所以才會直攻地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.89,0:03:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我得到有趣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.24,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算帶去地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.26,0:03:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.44,0:03:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重高達...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是,有人能使用嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.87,0:03:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是有你\n正在組織的新人類部隊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.49,0:03:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人,那是不實謠言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂,重高達給你使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明,你也到地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下官當然陪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.66,0:04:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能為哈曼大人\n當上忙的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.33,0:04:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必說客套話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿...真是順利\n平時放出太多假隕石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活該被我偷跑進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.78,0:04:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普露普露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.72,0:04:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胸口好緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.89,0:05:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是很舒服\n但怎麼會這樣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.19,0:05:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了,是那駕駛員關係!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達的駕駛員來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.43,0:05:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.92,0:05:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達的駕駛員來了\n不會有錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.74,0:05:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,這裏是宮殿\n你怎麼可以隨便亂跑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有急事,你別管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.08,0:05:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯的人真有活力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.41,0:05:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對,她是例外\n壞例子,你要當作沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒這麼厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.83,0:06:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去居住區一下\n波蕾小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.32,0:06:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種東西用搬運機送就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼盡叫我們做些無聊事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.46,0:06:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們好像螞蟻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,螞蟻比我們好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.33,0:06:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時還能找到甜點吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.61,0:06:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們得了重力失衡癥了\n差勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.43,0:06:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.46,0:06:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這混蛋!可惡,可惡,可惡,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准浪費食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.02,0:06:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,我受夠這種生活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.73,0:06:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.97,0:06:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在亞加瑪還好過這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.28,0:06:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回亞加瑪嗎?\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.14,0:06:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能,我們拿什麼臉回去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.81,0:06:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動動你的頭腦阿,若救出莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.87,0:06:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣別人就無話可說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.79,0:07:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,決定了,開始行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像有點累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.07,0:07:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00ffff&}請必須進入3區的人家快動作...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.01,0:07:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00ffff&}請必須進入3區的人家快動作...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.32,0:07:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00ffff&}請必須進入3區的人家快動作...{\c}\n好像香格里拉的高級區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.10,0:07:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過就是有一點不太好\n這裏沒有天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是來找我的吧,大哥哥\n咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.62,0:07:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是波蕾,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.28,0:07:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼我好?我們有見過面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.45,0:07:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭...你忘記了嗎?\Nㄟ!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.64,0:07:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,你認錯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.60,0:07:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等~~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在趕路,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!我們要在一起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.45,0:08:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手!很辛苦啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那個人很像捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能,不過有點像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是蘋果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.11,0:08:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉,驚擾大家了\n這個蘋果很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.21,0:08:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是這裏的老闆嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.08,0:08:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你吃的完嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.82,0:08:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你拿著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.55,0:08:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ㄚ~~~我要吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.71,0:08:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前我也來過這家店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.16,0:09:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣,亞古捷斯的街道很美吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.84,0:09:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時間應該帶你慢慢參觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.06,0:09:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是服飾店!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.23,0:09:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要買衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.91,0:09:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衣服?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.53,0:09:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,以後還要\n離開亞古捷斯一段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實應該添購衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!聽在那家店前面\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥哥叫什麼名子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.84,0:09:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,捷度.桑達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.44,0:09:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是第一殖民地\n香格里拉的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是土生土長的亞古捷斯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭一次這麼近看著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.73,0:09:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼認識我的?\n這樣說太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,確實奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.09,0:09:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.52,0:09:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.25,0:09:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下,剛見面就接吻太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.30,0:09:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是來找妹妹的,別妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.42,0:09:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找妹妹...不會是她吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想應該是她\n她在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.05,0:10:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.29,0:10:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要!還沒全部吃完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來吃完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.65,0:10:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我厲害,沾到臉頰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.36,0:10:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...這件應該很適合露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.93,0:10:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我還不知道她的三圍...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!怎麼了...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.74,0:10:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃是沒用的...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些蘋果怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賣給別的水果攤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個老闆真狠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經夠瓊\n還逼人買這麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是莉娜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.48,0:10:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!你在那裏做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,莫迪,有人在追我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!你在那裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.84,0:10:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.30,0:10:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躲是沒用的,立刻給我出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.91,0:10:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要蘋果,這個免費送你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.98,0:10:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點可惜...\n快點,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.11,0:11:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小偷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下車!這輛車被軍方徵收了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像剛才這樣一口氣吃光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.25,0:11:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不吃光我就不帶你去找她\n表演給我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.33,0:11:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.77,0:11:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照約定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我妹妹在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.02,0:11:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係,這樣比較舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.37,0:11:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想跑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暴走族嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.69,0:11:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯也有這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣才有朝氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊 這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.24,0:12:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!要得到那架MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.57,0:12:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!?你們在幹什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個MS我開走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個不是玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.32,0:12:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.89,0:12:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我操縱這種MS技術比捷度還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.87,0:12:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到哥哥了\n那個人一定是哥哥沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.78,0:12:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯的\n我們看到的人一定是捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.80,0:12:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.15,0:12:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開動MS的嚴重性嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.74,0:12:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為這樣亂玩\n不會受到懲罰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.61,0:12:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.55,0:12:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰在開動那個MS?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一群壞小孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.59,0:12:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是二男一女,對不對?\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.36,0:12:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!你再不下來\n別怪我對你使用體罰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說要動用體罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個怪小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不下去啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,踩死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.40,0:13:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要追上來,我就饒你一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艙門關不起來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.57,0:13:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開關是這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.05,0:13:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這架MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒裝艙門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.66,0:13:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣子無法出去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,途中在搶太空衣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.79,0:13:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?怎麼有MS在市區走動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.19,0:13:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!!!是上次捉弄我們的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!沒打中!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.04,0:13:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手,殺人是不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道他們對我們多惡劣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.65,0:13:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們該死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.85,0:13:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開MS攻擊一般人太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放走,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的作法太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們全是卑鄙小人\n不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.07,0:14:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害!跟宮殿一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.48,0:14:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜真的再這裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.64,0:14:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,快點走啊\n喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.15,0:14:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你們了\n是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.74,0:14:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會是這所宮殿的公主吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個感覺...是馬沙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.69,0:14:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...不對,是誰呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.15,0:14:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.47,0:14:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在感覺不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.97,0:14:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺不到?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.29,0:14:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗個澡睡一下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我就可以感覺到,明白嗎??
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.83,0:14:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我去洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.80,0:15:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑,真是的\n波蕾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.50,0:15:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.10,0:15:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜真的在這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.86,0:15:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說出所屬的組織跟密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.77,0:15:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是...再見!\n別跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.52,0:15:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.10,0:15:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打不開\n在這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度...人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.43,0:16:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛,好痛,好痛~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.01,0:16:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼在這裏種玫瑰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.19,0:16:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道...這小孩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.51,0:16:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來問你,你是哪裏的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.34,0:16:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,這地方太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.61,0:16:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你屬於什麼機關?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想裝傻,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.79,0:16:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.10,0:16:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再問一次\n你屬於什麼機關?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.25,0:16:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你問我,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次不是恐嚇阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.72,0:16:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別...開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.87,0:16:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不說嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃向宮殿那裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋,別逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.72,0:17:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以大欺小,太差勁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道我們吃了多少苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.39,0:17:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你吃的好還有鋼琴彈\n讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.44,0:17:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要踩死你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?比查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.52,0:17:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉桿掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想個辦法阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒辦法停下來阿\n快停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.73,0:17:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.77,0:17:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我屬亞加瑪,知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪,果然是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯被
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.71,0:17:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪的人闖進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.40,0:17:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.52,0:17:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋才不跑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.44,0:18:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女人是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼看到奇怪的景象?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.24,0:18:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我在月月看到的那艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.21,0:18:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了,莉娜在那裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.08,0:18:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔\n你有沒有看到在這裏的隕石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.48,0:18:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隕石?那東西礙事,丟掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.07,0:18:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦!!丟在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.91,0:18:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艙口的另一邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.91,0:18:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艙口的另一邊...怎麼會這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.04,0:18:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒穿太空衣想去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.50,0:18:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏的另一邊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.71,0:19:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道有沒有空氣?在哪裏?\n找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快沒空氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜一定還再那艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她跑到哪裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去哪裏?捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是波蕾嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,答對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.28,0:19:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會操作MS嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼跑出來的,捷度?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.74,0:19:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你妹妹在宮殿的後院...\n咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她在地落的MS裏頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.63,0:19:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能?你騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.86,0:19:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管你妹妹,和我玩,出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.52,0:19:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑了,我沒有穿太空衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也沒有,這樣很公平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.58,0:19:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不公平!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.74,0:20:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.15,0:20:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想妨礙我與捷度?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.14,0:20:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手,別打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.33,0:20:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要生氣,我想跟捷度玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.86,0:20:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.32,0:20:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手,波蕾,不然我真的生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.31,0:20:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,為什麼...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.31,0:20:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.08,0:20:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.23,0:20:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.33,0:20:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.55,0:21:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,你不應該殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.19,0:21:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這麼天真的女孩\n不該當駕駛員的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.10,0:21:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.66,0:21:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想跟你玩阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.79,0:21:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾,別太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.10,0:21:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度很討厭\n為什麼不陪我玩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.33,0:21:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你坐MS我才不陪你玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.84,0:21:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭,很討厭你阿,我討厭捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.93,0:21:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!波蕾!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.21,0:22:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了,我找古利明安慰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.01,0:22:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度是大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連這麼小的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.75,0:22:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都被培訓成MS駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.85,0:22:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜還在亞古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.90,0:22:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次我一定要救出她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.78,0:22:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你替我轉告亞加瑪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.66,0:23:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以ZZ作為見面禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入亞古捷斯也是為了莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.74,0:23:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 沒想到比查和蒙德會把ZZ帶出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.81,0:24:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後 亞加瑪要測試新的主炮\n被設定為目標的怎麼是我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.16,0:24:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒醒啊 波蕾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.76,0:24:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.01,0:24:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾與亞古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.09,0:24:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別攻擊啊！布拉度艦長

